---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import About from '../components/About.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Your Akashic Guide | Akashic Record Readings"
  description="Learn about your Akashic Record reader's journey, certifications, and approach to accessing the Akashic Records for spiritual guidance."
>
  <div class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-accent-200 to-white inline-block text-transparent bg-clip-text">
          About Me & My Approach
        </h1>
        <div class="divider mx-auto w-24"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <About />
  
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 relative">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div data-aos="fade-right">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-accent-200 to-white inline-block text-transparent bg-clip-text">
            My Journey to the Akashic Records
          </h2>
          <div class="divider w-24 mb-6"></div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            My connection to the spiritual realm began in childhood, when I experienced vivid dreams and intuitive insights that seemed beyond my years. It wasn't until a profound meditation experience in my mid-twenties that I discovered the Akashic Records and realized I had been unconsciously accessing them all along.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            After this awakening, I devoted myself to the formal study of Akashic Record reading under several master teachers. I completed certifications with the Center for Akashic Studies and the International Institute of Akashic Records, developing a unique approach that balances traditional wisdom with contemporary understanding.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            In my 15+ years as a practitioner, I've conducted over 2,000 readings, helping clients from all walks of life uncover their soul's purpose, heal relationship patterns, and align with their highest path. My greatest joy is witnessing the transformation that occurs when someone connects with the profound wisdom of their own Records.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div data-aos="fade-left">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-accent-200 to-white inline-block text-transparent bg-clip-text">
            My Approach to Readings
          </h2>
          <div class="divider w-24 mb-6"></div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            I believe that the Akashic Records are not just a repository of past events, but a living, dynamic field of potential and possibility. When I access your Records, I'm connecting with the energetic blueprint of your soul—past, present, and future possibilities.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            My readings focus on empowerment rather than prediction. Instead of telling you what will happen, I help you understand the energetic patterns at play and how you can consciously work with them to create your desired experiences.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            I approach each session with reverence, compassion, and a commitment to the highest good. The information I share is delivered with care and always includes practical guidance for integration into your daily life.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Whether you're seeking clarity on your life purpose, understanding relationship patterns, or healing from past traumas, I'm here to facilitate a transformative journey into the wisdom of your soul.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 relative bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-primary-950/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-8" data-aos="fade-up">
          <div class="bg-primary-900/50 p-3 rounded-lg inline-block mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-400">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9 4.5a.75.75 0 01.721.544l.813 2.846a3.75 3.75 0 002.576 2.576l2.846.813a.75.75 0 010 1.442l-2.846.813a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576 2.576l-.813 2.846a.75.75 0 01-1.442 0l-.813-2.846a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576-2.576l-2.846-.813a.75.75 0 010-1.442l2.846-.813A3.75 3.75 0 007.466 7.89l.813-2.846A.75.75 0 019 4.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-medium text-white mb-4">Certifications</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
            <li>• Certificación de hipnosis clinica</li>
            <li>• Certificación Quantum Healing Hypnosis(QHHT) de DOlores Cannon</li>
            <li>• Certificación Reiki 1, 2, 3</li>
            <li>• Certificación Reiki Master</li>
            <li>• Certificación de lectura Registros Akashicos</li>
            <li>• Certificación de limpieza Registros Akashicos por Adrian Lee</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="bg-primary-900/50 p-3 rounded-lg inline-block mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-400">
              <path d="M11.7 2.805a.75.75 0 01.6 0A60.65 60.65 0 0122.83 8.72a.75.75 0 01-.231 1.337 49.949 49.949 0 00-9.902 3.912l-.003.002-.34.18a.75.75 0 01-.707 0A50.009 50.009 0 007.5 12.174v-.224c0-.131.067-.248.172-.311a54.614 54.614 0 014.653-2.52.75.75 0 00-.65-1.352 56.129 56.129 0 00-4.78 2.589 1.858 1.858 0 00-.859 1.228 49.803 49.803 0 00-4.634-1.527.75.75 0 01-.231-1.337A60.653 60.653 0 0111.7 2.805z" />
